title: Narayanni's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, International, Organic, Buffet, African, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. South African Indian cuisine in a casual fine setting. Uses organic and local ingredients; no dairy in the sauces, so the vegetarian items are also vegan suitable. Tuesday is an inexpensive vegan night where the buffet features all vegan appetizers, salads, main entrees, and desserts.
